    "Welcome aboard, {client}! Here's what to expect:\n\n1. Calendly for our first sync: {calendly}\n2. Banking info below (if paying by wire)\n3. Slack channel invite coming in 24h\n4. Progress demos every Thursday\n\nLooking forward to working together!": {
      "comment": "Usage scenario example",
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome aboard, {client}! Here's what to expect:\n\n1. Calendly for our first sync: {calendly}\n2. Banking info below (if paying by wire)\n3. Slack channel invite coming in 24h\n4. Progress demos every Thursday\n\nLooking forward to working together!"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome aboard, {client}! Here's what to expect:\n\n1. Calendly for our first sync: {calendly}\n2. Banking info below (if paying by wire)\n3. Slack channel invite coming in 24h\n4. Progress demos every Thursday\n\nLooking forward to working together!"
          }
        },
        "id": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Selamat bergabung, {client}! Berikut yang akan terjadi:\n\n1. Calendly untuk sync pertama: {calendly}\n2. Info rekening di bawah (jika bayar via transfer)\n3. Undangan channel Slack dalam 24 jam\n4. Demo progress setiap Kamis\n\nSemoga kerjasama lancar!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
